import './TableTitle.css'

const TableTitle = () => {

    return (
        <thead className="title">
            <tr>
                <th>Titulo</th>
                <th>Data de Criacao</th>
                <th>Data de Finalizacao</th>
                <th>Responsavel</th>
                <th>Prioridade</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
    )
}

export default TableTitle
